- Use **Prettier defaults** (single quotes, 2-space indent, semicolons ON)
- **File names**: kebab-case folders, camelCase files
- **Variables** are descriptive, e.g. isLoading, hasError, reviewCount
- **Conventional Commits** prefixes (feat:, fix:, docs:) max 60 chars
